# Trivy ignore file for gitops-demo-app
#
# CVEs listed here are acknowledged, reviewed, and accepted.
# Each entry must include: the CVE ID, the package affected,
# the reason for acceptance, and a review date.
#
# Format: one CVE per line. Blank lines and # comments allowed.
#
# Example (remove if empty):
# CVE-2024-XXXXX  # ip package via bundled npm — Node team not patching, low exploitability in our context — reviewed 2026-04-23
